trans-unit.source: Learn how to use Azure Redis Cache
trans-unit.target: Learn how to use Azure Redis Cache

trans-unit.source: This topic provides a list of Azure Redis Cache samples, covering scenarios such as connecting to a cache, reading and writing data to and from a cache, and using the ASP.NET Redis Cache providers.
trans-unit.target: This topic provides a list of Azure Redis Cache samples, covering scenarios such as connecting to a cache, reading and writing data to and from a cache, and using the ASP.NET Redis Cache providers.

trans-unit.source: Some of the samples are downloadable projects, and some provide step-by-step guidance and include code snippets but do not link to a downloadable project.
trans-unit.target: Some of the samples are downloadable projects, and some provide step-by-step guidance and include code snippets but do not link to a downloadable project.

trans-unit.source: The samples in this section show the basics of connecting to an Azure Redis Cache instance and reading and writing data to the cache using a variety of languages and Redis clients.
trans-unit.target: The samples in this section show the basics of connecting to an Azure Redis Cache instance and reading and writing data to the cache using a variety of languages and Redis clients.

trans-unit.source: The <linkText>Bandwidth monitor</linkText><title></title> sample allows you to monitor the bandwidth used on the client.
trans-unit.target: The <linkText>Bandwidth monitor</linkText><title></title> sample allows you to monitor the bandwidth used on the client.

trans-unit.source: To measure the bandwidth, run the sample on the cache client machine, make calls to the cache, and observe the bandwidth reported by the bandwidth monitor sample.
trans-unit.target: To measure the bandwidth, run the sample on the cache client machine, make calls to the cache, and observe the bandwidth reported by the bandwidth monitor sample.
